<h2>Product Image Upload </h2>
<p> This page allows you to select and upload product  images of all types. Image types that come with an out-of-the-box Cartweaver solution are Expanded, Full, Small, and Thumbnail. The image upload will only allow web compatible image files to be uploaded. Those image files ending in .gif, .jpg, .jpeg or .png.</p>
<p>Once the Image is selected and uploaded the appropriate image name field will be updated with the name of the image file that was uploaded. </p>
